No. 5,

Misc.

Triplett v. Iowa. Herbert S. French for petitioner. Norman A. Erbe, Attorney General of Iowa, Raphael R. R. Dvorak, First Assistant Attorney General, and Don C. Swanson, Assistant Attorney General, for respondent.

Motion for leave to proceed in forma pauperis and petition for writ of cer-tiorari to the Supreme Court of Iowa granted.
